{"title":"祖国之窗","authors":["宫玺"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国之窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫玺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们连队俱乐部的墙上，张贴着许多信件，我们称它作“祖国之窗”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——引自手记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张又一张；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红、白、蓝、绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像鲜花开放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色的，来自塞北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里漫山遍野白茫茫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是云，不是雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是牧羊姑娘在牧羊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声饱含幸福情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行行散发奶油香。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张又一张；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像无数长绸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系着遥远的家乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的，来自钢城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自鞍钢武钢和包钢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来了，钟响了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红波滚滚通天亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸着炼钢工的汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字如钢响当当！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张又一张；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方飞了来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾着风的翅膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的，来自江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里水田细雨染绿秧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋来了，枫叶红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金稻漫天卷夕阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片公社丰收景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片农村新气象！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张又一张；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像朵朵彩云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘进了营房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的，来自大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自海鸥追随的船舱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收网了，返航了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银鱼如山映月光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔家的话如东海水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句颂歌一个浪。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张又一张；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张金色的在中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同美丽的凤凰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这金色的，来自北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自党中央和毛主席住的地方；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门，生瑞气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想闪金光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着首都人民的祝福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信笺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着领袖的关怀和期望！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"构成祖国的图样；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的脚步和呼吸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战士心中引起巨大的回响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明亮的眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着亲爱的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗大的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧握住战斗的枪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}